room_title: Escape room "Ghost Ship" by 60out Escape Rooms in Los Angeles
room_description: Many years ago a curse was put on this ship and the whole crew for their sins. Since that wretched night, they have been capturing people at sea and holding them captive with the hope that they might be the ones to help break the spell, but no one has even come close. After you are caught, can you release everyone from this dark spell, or will you become a part of the cursed crew like so many before you?
